{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-44-pentagon-numbers","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-1-to-100","demoType":null,"title":"Izazov 44: brojevi pentagona","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Brojevi za pentagone se generišu korišćenjem formule, P<sub>n</sub>=<code>n</code>(3<code>n</code>−1)/2. Prvih deset brojeva pentagona su:</p>\n<p>1, 5, 12, 22, 35, 51, 70, 92, 117, 145, ...</p>\n<p>Izgleda da P<sub>4</sub> + P<sub>7</sub> = 22 + 70 = 92 = P<sub>8</sub>. Međutim, njihova razlika, 70 − 22 = 48, nije pentagon.</p>\n<p>Potražite par brojeva za pentagon, P<sub>j</sub> na P<sub>k</sub>, čiji je zbir i razlika pentagon i D = |P<sub>k</sub> − P<sub>j</sub>| je najmanji; Koja je vrednost D?</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f3981000cf542c50feab","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302111,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-44-pentagon-numbers"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function pentagonNumbers() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\npentagonNumbers();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>pentagonNumbers()</code> trebalo bi da vrati broj.</p>","testString":"assert(typeof pentagonNumbers() === 'number');"},{"text":"<p><code>pentagonNumbers()</code> treba vratiti 5482660.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(pentagonNumbers(), 5482660);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-1-to-100","dashedName":"problem-44-pentagon-numbers","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-1-to-100","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-45-triangular-pentagonal-and-hexagonal","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-43-sub-string-divisibility","id":"5900f3981000cf542c50feab","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function arrangedProbability(limit) {\n  // Based on https://www.mathblog.dk/project-euler-100-blue-discs-two-blue/\n  let blue = 15;\n  let discs = 21;\n\n  while (discs < limit) {\n    const nextBlue = 3 * blue + 2 * discs - 2;\n    const nextDiscs = 4 * blue + 3 * discs - 3;\n\n    blue = nextBlue;\n    discs = nextDiscs;\n  }\n  return blue;\n}","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-44-pentagon-numbers"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}